Purpose
-------
This is a plugin for Quicksilver. It makes Opera (and other browsers) act nice together.

Features
--------
* Adds a catalog with the bookmarks and searches of Opera
* Adds a "Operas current web page" proxy object
* Adds an "Open with Opera" action
* Adds a couple of scripts for copying and moving URLs between Opera, Safari and Firefox
* Browse into Opera to get current open tabs

Requirements
------------
Quicksilver, Opera 11.

Compile Requirements
--------------------
XCode, Quicksilver in its developper version
See http://lipidity.com/apple/quicksilver-plugins-in-objective-c/
A big dose of patience, this is a hack together

Credits
-------
